modules.description: Parses SGF FF[4] files, extracting game records with support for UTF-8 encoding. Processes game trees, properties, and node attributes using custom data structures. Enables retrieval of move sequences, player names, and game metadata for analysis or display.

Parses SGF content from strings, channels, or files into a structured collection of game trees. Works with nested data types like nodes, sequences, and properties, each representing elements of a game record. Provides pretty-printing functions to format these structures for human-readable output.
